MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 468091314}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 885bba7728ad07549a93f95d5f844caf, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialoguePanel: {fileID: 879880741}
  NPCName: {fileID: 1600727701}
  playerInteractionPanel: {fileID: 731005218}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 1331868485}
  defaultDialogue:
  - Hello, Tokyo, how you doin'?
  - Listen, I heard you picked something up for Berlin from the chests, right?
  - "I don\u2019t need this item \u2014 but you will."
  - It's in one of the metal chests in the underground.
  - But before taking it, you need to hack the chest to open it.
  - So I figured maybe you could use the laptop for that.
  - The chest has its own code, and it should be written on a piece of paper.
  - "I saw the paper here, on the second floor \u2014 so go and find it."
  - "Since it\u2019s one specific chest, you\u2019ll also need the layout of the
    metal chests."
  - That plan should be on a table in the office to the right of where Nairobi always
    goes.
  - After that, you can finally grab the item. Good luck!
  inactiveDialogue:
  - I'm busy right now, sorry.
  relatedQuestName: Hack the chest
  allowedQuestName: Talk to Stockholm
  contButton: {fileID: 2138084966}
  wordSpeed: 0.03
  playerIsClose: 0
